comment:
* Exception thrown by the service when a failed HTTP request is the cause of a failed API call.
 *
 * @hide

variables.name: ERROR_REDIRECTION
variables.comment: * Error code indicating that the service received an HTTP 3xx status code.

variables.name: ERROR_CLIENT
variables.comment: * Error code indicating that the service received an HTTP 4xx status code.

variables.name: ERROR_TOO_MANY_REQUESTS
variables.comment: * Error code indicating that the user has sent too many requests in a given amount of time and * the service received an HTTP * 429 status code.

variables.name: ERROR_SERVER
variables.comment: * Error code indicating that the service received an HTTP 5xx status code.

variables.name: ERROR_OTHER
variables.comment: Error code indicating another type of error was encountered.

methods.name: public int getErrorCode()
methods.comment: * @return the {@link ErrorCode} indicating what caused the HTTP request to fail.
